## Limitations

The analysis is limited by the availability of data up to October 2023, and the reliance on publicly available information. The insights are based on articles and discussions that may not cover all aspects of the rental car industry's pricing strategies. Additionally, the dynamic nature of the industry means that factors influencing prices can change rapidly, potentially affecting the relevance of the findings over time.

